reviewText: My grandsons and I love Tom and Jerry so much, and this DVD was great!
Got it faster than I had expected! My son loved it!
I like the tom and jerry cartoon.
This is what I was looking for
We have volume 2 so I think we have a lot
Similar to what I said about other collections like it, It's short and sweet. The price is low but to relive the epic feud between Tom and Jerry is well worth it.
